desc: At Flee 100, we believe in expressing one's fresh and empowered lifestyle, or as we refer to it, staying Flee, 100 percent of the time. Join the Flee Fam and discover the vibrations of One Love, unity, and the power of community

layout.text: Flee 100 dedicates itself to be a fashion brand that facilitates a 20/20 style vision for the needs of the younger generation. It's an American brand that strives to make our customers feel unique....it's a lifestyle.
